      <title>爱尔兰议会投票任命西蒙·哈里斯为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/irish-parliament-votes-to-appoint-simon-harris-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在利奥·瓦拉德卡意外辞职三周后，爱尔兰立法者投票选举西蒙·哈里斯为下一任总理。 37 岁的他将成为爱尔兰最年轻的总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/irish-parliament-votes-to-appoint-simon-harris-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:19:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟通过风力探测器加大对中国绿色科技的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/eu-ramps-up-pressure-on-china-s-green-tech-with-wind-power-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟努力将欧盟转变为绿色经济之际，欧盟加大了对中国清洁技术投资的压力，可能会排挤其当地供应商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/eu-ramps-up-pressure-on-china-s-green-tech-with-wind-power-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚国王呼吁在假期前团结一致应对袜子纠纷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/malaysia-king-calls-for-unity-ahead-of-holidays-amid-socks-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚国王易卜拉欣·伊斯坎达尔建议该国领导人不要在种族和宗教问题上发表“极端观点”，因为他试图结束因销售印有“阿拉”字样的袜子而引发的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/malaysia-king-calls-for-unity-ahead-of-holidays-amid-socks-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:42:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度法院驳回德里首席部长反对逮捕的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/india-court-rejects-delhi-chief-minister-s-plea-against-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度一家法院维持了对德里首席部长阿尔文德·凯杰里瓦尔的逮捕，他是反对派联盟的主要领导人，该联盟正在与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党进行全国民意调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/india-court-rejects-delhi-chief-minister-s-plea-against-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:23:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼官员认为，随着增长的保持，意大利的债务将会上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meloni-team-sees-italy-2024-growth-of-1-but-with-debt-rising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的政府展望，意大利的债务负担将再次开始上升，该展望还坚称意大利经济将在 2024 年实现超出大多数预测的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meloni-team-sees-italy-2024-growth-of-1-but-with-debt-rising</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人权法院称瑞士公民在气候问题上失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/swiss-failed-citizens-on-climate-change-human-rights-court-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲人权法院在一项具有里程碑意义的裁决中表示，瑞士未能保护其公民免受气候变化的破坏，这一裁决可能会对整个欧洲大陆产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/swiss-failed-citizens-on-climate-change-human-rights-court-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:13:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡梅伦游说老对手特朗普解锁美国对乌克兰的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/cameron-lobbies-trump-to-break-us-roadblocks-to-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦在佛罗里达州与唐纳德·特朗普举行会议，英国试图说服总统候选人的共和党盟友停止阻挠美国向乌克兰提供更多援助的承诺，两人过去曾在英国脱欧和北约问题上发生冲突。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/cameron-lobbies-trump-to-break-us-roadblocks-to-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其和以色列就加沙紧张局势升级的贸易问题互相指责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/turkey-restricts-exports-to-israel-over-gaza-air-drop-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其因反对以色列放弃对加沙地带援助的提议而决定限制对以色列的出口，此举引起了迅速的报复性反应，进一步加剧了这两个曾经的军事盟友之间本已紧张的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/turkey-restricts-exports-to-israel-over-gaza-air-drop-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西弗吉尼亚州禁止花旗银行和汇丰银行签订有关石油的银行合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/west-virginia-bars-citi-hsbc-from-banking-contracts-over-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西弗吉尼亚州财政部长宣布，他限制四家金融服务公司提供州银行服务，因为他说它们“抵制”化石燃料行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/west-virginia-bars-citi-hsbc-from-banking-contracts-over-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 17:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙与其他欧盟国家一起计划终止黄金签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/spain-to-end-golden-visa-program-for-real-estate-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙计划结束针对外国购房者的所谓黄金签证计划，以增加当地人可获得的经济适用住房的数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/spain-to-end-golden-visa-program-for-real-estate-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:55:14 GMT</pubDate>
